{
  "stem": "17526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from there, they put us on cattle cars, and we were taken to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the way, we were bombed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From the-- we ran out, we jumped out of the cattle cars, and we were hiding underneath the cars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll never forget that scene, either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How we wound up in Buchenwald, there was another together, another mix of all camps from all over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were so many numerous camps in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And people hear of Auschwitz and Buchenwald, but there were so many other killing-- I mean death factories that may not have been so well-documented and well-written.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were camps all over the place, all over Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from Buchenwald, we were segregated again, and we were shipped to Spaichingen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My brother was-- my brother, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had heard-- then we were separated towards the end [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were still together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Spaichingen was absolutely a killer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] There were very few people who survived there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's another person that lived in Philadelphia, my brother and myself-- myself and this other person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did we find out?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, years after the war, we were summoned to the German consulate here, and they were trying to get us to-- summoned to be witnesses for a Nazi trial.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They caught somebody that was an official in-- in Spaichingen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And knowing from our documents that we were in Spaichingen, could we attest to it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were drilled at the German consulate here for two days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after the second day, the guy that interrogated me told me, if you are interested in seeing somebody else that lives here in Philadelphia, I'll give you his telephone number.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got in touch with him and we made contact.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
